info.title: Maintenance Item
info.description: This API allows you to read, create, and update maintenance items. The request contains all the information that is necessary to read, create, and update maintenance items. If the input in the request is not as expected, the system displays appropriate error or warning messages in the response.

x-sap-shortText: Read, create, and update maintenance items using this synchronous inbound service
